title: Per Capita Personal Consumption Expenditures: Goods: Durable Goods: Other Durable Goods for Rocky Mountain BEA Region
notes:
Personal consumption expenditures of a given area divided by the resident population of the area.

Purchases of jewelry and watches, therapeutic appliances and equipment, educational books, luggage and similar personal items, and telephone and facsimile equipment.For more information about this release go to http://www.bea.gov/newsreleases/regional/pce/pce_newsrelease.htm.
